# IntelliForge AI OS ‚Äî Landing Page
# Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript strict mode
- Tailwind CSS with custom IF design tokens (tailwind.config.ts)
- Neon PostgreSQL via `@neondatabase/serverless` (waitlist)
- Vercel Analytics (`@vercel/analytics`)
- lucide-react for icons
- JetBrains Mono for code traces, Inter for UI

## Design Tokens
Tailwind tokens (tailwind.config.ts):
- `if-dark`     #0f172a  ‚Äî page background
- `if-text`     #e2e8f0  ‚Äî body text
- `if-text-dim` #94a3b8  ‚Äî muted text
- `if-green`    #10b981  ‚Äî success / eval layer

Brand palette (inline in components + globals.css):
- `if-indigo`  #4f46e5  ‚Äî primary brand
- `if-purple`  #7c3aed  ‚Äî secondary
- `if-cyan`    #06b6d4  ‚Äî accent / India layer
- `if-orange`  #f97316  ‚Äî India layer

## CSS Classes (globals.css)
- `.text-gradient-if`  ‚Äî indigo‚Üípurple‚Üícyan gradient text
- `.text-gradient-cyan` ‚Äî cyan gradient text
- `.glass-card`        ‚Äî frosted glass card
- `.glass-card-indigo` ‚Äî indigo-tinted glass
- `.glass-card-cyan`   ‚Äî cyan-tinted glass
- `.btn-primary`       ‚Äî indigo gradient CTA button
- `.btn-secondary`     ‚Äî ghost button
- `.tag-pill`          ‚Äî small pill label (use with .tag-indigo etc)
- `.eyebrow`           ‚Äî uppercase section label
- `.code-trace`        ‚Äî JetBrains Mono code trace text
- `.harness-layer`     ‚Äî left-bordered layer row

## Components
- `Navbar`       ‚Äî fixed top nav with scroll detection
- `Hero`         ‚Äî animated harness layer stack + code traces
- `Architecture` ‚Äî 5-layer stack + 8-package SDK table
- `Products`     ‚Äî IF portfolio as ForgeOS Cloud tenants
- `Roadmap`      ‚Äî 5 build phases with timeline
- `Pricing`      ‚Äî 4 tiers in INR (Free / ‚Çπ2,999 / ‚Çπ9,999 / Enterprise)
- `Waitlist`     ‚Äî email capture with role selector
- `Footer`       ‚Äî links + brand
- `CopyButton`   ‚Äî clipboard copy for docs page

## Lib
- `lib/db.ts`       ‚Äî Neon client + `insertWaitlistEntry()`
- `lib/aisensy.ts`  ‚Äî optional WhatsApp confirmation on waitlist submit
- `lib/packages.ts` ‚Äî shared SDK package metadata (Architecture + Docs)

## Environment Variables (.env.local)
```bash
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...          # Neon ‚Äî required for waitlist
AISENSY_API_KEY=...                    # optional ‚Äî WhatsApp confirmation
AISENSY_CAMPAIGN_NAME=aios_waitlist_confirmation
```

## Data Layer
- Database: Neon PostgreSQL
- Table: `aios_waitlist (id, name, email, role, use_case, created_at)`
- API route: `POST /api/waitlist` ‚Üí `lib/db.ts` + fire-and-forget `lib/aisensy.ts`
- Do NOT use Supabase for this project

