## Naming Conventions
- All IF products: PascalCase (AwaazOS, ForgeAhead, HridLink)
- npm packages: lowercase-kebab (@intelliforge/harness-core)
- API routes: /api/waitlist
- Postgres tables: snake_case (aios_waitlist)
- All INR amounts as integer paise internally (‚Çπ2,999 = 299900 paise)
- Dates: DD/MM/YYYY for display, ISO 8601 for storage
- Phones: E.164 format

## Do not change
- The 5-layer harness architecture (matches IF-RES-2026-017)
- The 8-package SDK names (they match the research spec)
- The INR pricing tiers (‚Çπ2,999 / ‚Çπ9,999)
- The IF monogram "IF" styling
